Codeigniter Image helper
========================

Generate image thumbnails in views templates by:
    image_thumb("http://i.ytimg.com/vi/the0KZLEacs/hqdefault.jpg", 90, 120)
or
    image_thumb("images/hqdefault.jpg", 90, 120)

Parameters
----------
    @param string  $path Path to the image file, relative to CI webroot or an URL
    @param integer $width Image of returned image
    @param integer $height Height of returned image
    @param boolean $aspect Maintain aspect ratio (default: true)
    @param array   $htmlAttributes Array of HTML attributes.
    @param boolean $return Wheter this method should return a value or output it. This overrides AUTO_OUTPUT. (default: true)

Return
------
void if `$return` is false, else return `<img />`

Installtion
----------
Place this file within helpers folder.
